data.description: Located in the heart of Alamo Heights, this beautiful fully remodeled home boasts oversized bedrooms, multiple large windows throughout, your own private courtyard for entertaining, and all the character and charm that comes with being a part of this prestigious neighborhood. Ranked one of the best school districts in the State, you'll be able to walk your kids to and from Cambridge Elementary and skip the carpool line! From the Community Garden, Nature Trails, Bark Park, and Community Pool, you and your family will never be stuck inside wondering what to do.  These are just a few of the many things you'll love about this stunning home in its prime location! Schedule your private showing today!
